text: Duvan-Mechetlino () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Duvan-Mechetlinsky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 681 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 32 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Duvan-Mechetlino
